  "description": "From the manufacturer Silverline 395010 Drain Unblocker 6m x 6mm Diameter Manufacturer's Description Used for the effective cleaning of sinks, basins, baths, showers and drains and other small diameter pipework, the Silverline Drain Unblocker features a flexible spiral 12mm diameter rod which is hand-fed into the drain from the rotatable plastic container. It is then pulled back out of the drain, removing stubborn blockages and debris in one simple process. The plastic container holds the waste, avoiding spilling debris on to clean kitchen and bathroom surfaces. The rotating handle easily eliminates hard to shift blocks and the ergonomic pistol grip allows comfortable handling. This simple-to-use yet highly effective tool is a toolbox essential for any household, DIYer or plumber. - Extendable, hand-fed 6m x 6mm dia spiral rod - Straight 12mm dia auger - Rotating handle - Ergonomic pistol grip - Used for removing stubborn blockages and clearing drains Technical Specifications Diameter: 5.8mm dia, tip 12mm dia Handle diameter: 120 x 28 x 44mm Handle material: Polypropylene Material primary construction: Spring steel Product dimensions (H x L x W): 220 x 250 x 160mm Product weight: 0.910kg Key Features For cleaning sinks, basins, baths, showers and drains Extendable, hand-fed 6m x 6mm dia spiral rod Ergonomic pistol grip",
